Kevin Symons https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Kevin_Symons 0 Kevin William Symons (born February 2, 1971 in Highland Park, Illinois) is an American actor, who is best known for role as Dr. Kevin Adams in the television series Darcy's Wild Life. His other television credits include Joan of Arcadia, iCarly, Medium, Models, Inc., Sabrina, the Teenage Witch, Veronica Mars, The West Wing and Parks and Recreation. As well as recurring roles in the soap operas, Passions, The Bold and the Beautiful, and ABC Network's Desperate Housewives.
